# Agent Foundry Orchestrator

Plan -> execute -> verify with the local daemon on port 8765.

- `agent-foundry plan "<prompt>"` — rank skills
- `agent-foundry run "<prompt>"` — plan + execute top match
- `agent-foundry doctor` — health check
- `agent-foundry status` — routing accuracy, cost

Always check `agent-foundry doctor` before assuming the daemon is running.
The daemon is lazy-started; first command may take ~1s to boot.
Data stays in `~/.config/agent-foundry/executions.db`.
